A '''party school''' is a term used to refer to colleges, universities, or any institution of higher learning in which there exists a culture of ribaldry and licentiousness amongst the student population [[http://encarta.msn.com/college_article_partyheartyschools/that_party_the_heartiest.html]]. The term is not used mututally exclusively with a school that has a strong academic program (that is, a school can have a strong academic program and still be properly called a "party school"), though party schools often tend to be schools that do not have strong academic programs.

